6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ClickUp AI and Todoist share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Collaboration. Where ClickUp AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Notes and Automation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ClickUp AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Todoist scores 8/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both ClickUp AI and Todoist offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. ClickUp AI's free tier and Todoist's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
